## ğŸ“¦ Features

- ğŸ” Secure HTTPS deployment
- ğŸ“ Upload and store employee images in S3
- ğŸ§¾ Store employee details in SQL database
- ğŸ” Nginx reverse proxy for better performance
- ğŸ§¼ Clean and modular deployment setup

